## Bitcoin under Gentoo Linux

Check out the [Overlay](https://gitlab.com/bitcoin/gentoo) for ebuilds. Setup instructions can be found [here](https://gitlab.com/bitcoin/gentoo/blob/master/README) or simply type "layman -a bitcoin" to add the overlay.

